text: Christian Jesus González Nodal (born January 11, 1999) is a Mexican singer- songwriter and guitarist. His debut studio album, Me Dejé Llevar (2017), had positive reviews and became his well known work. Nodal has won three Latin Grammy Awards. ==References== Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican singer-songwriters Category:Mexican musicians Category:Pianists Category:Mexican guitarists Category:People from Sonora
